PRIVACY POLICY

Last updated: July 21, 2026

This Privacy Policy describes how CFA Level I Learner ("we," "our," or "the App") handles your information when you use our mobile application.

1. NO DATA COLLECTION

CFA Level I Learner does not collect, transmit, or share any personal information, usage data, or device identifiers. The App is designed to function entirely offline with no network communication.

2. LOCAL STORAGE ONLY

All data you create within the App is stored exclusively on your device using local storage (IndexedDB). This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to us or any third party. The App stores the following types of data locally:

- Quiz and mock exam results (scores, dates, topic performance)
- Reading completion progress
- Study notes you create
- Bookmarks you save
- Study time logs
- Language preference (English, French, or Spanish)

3. NO THIRD-PARTY SERVICES

The App does not integrate with any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services. Specifically, the App does not use:

- Firebase or any Google Cloud services
- Google Analytics or any analytics SDK
- Advertising networks
- Crash reporting tools
- Any remote APIs or servers

All study content (lessons, questions, and UI text) is bundled with the App and loaded from local files. No content is fetched from the internet.

4. NO USER ACCOUNTS

The App does not require or support user registration, login, or authentication. There are no user accounts, and we have no ability to identify individual users.

5. NO CHILDREN'S DATA

The App is designed for adult learners preparing for the CFA Level I examination. It does not knowingly collect any data from children under the age of 13.

6. DATA DELETION

You can delete all stored data at any time by going to Settings > Clear All Data within the App. Additionally, you can clear the App's data through your device's application settings.

7. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted within the App or on the App's store listing. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

8. CONTACT US

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact the developer at the email address listed on the Google Play Store listing for this App or Email: ivanng611@gmail.com

9. DISCLAIMER

CFA Level I Learner is an unofficial study aid and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by the CFA Institute. All CFA Institute content and trademarks are the property of the CFA Institute.
